title: Shein, Chanel, Hermès Buck Apparel Market Slowdown
body: Data and analytics company GlobalData said that Shein's market share has grown by 0.24 percentage points since 2023, beating out the likes of Nike, H&M and Louis Vuitton.

title: Coach's Owner Tapestry Files Trademark Infringement Suit Against Shein
body: Like its chief fast-fashion rival Temu, Shein is facing multiple cases of trademark infringement by companies and artists.
